high_descs: Turn around and walk forward until before you reach the fridge then turn to the left  to face the black toaster.
Grab the knife that is next to the black toaster.
Turn around and walk a few steps until you pass the kitchen faucet then turn right  and walk forwards facing the zinc.
Put the knife inside the orange round glass next to the white mug.
Grab the orange round glass and turn to the left.
Walk forward before reaching the microwave then turn right and walk to the kitchen counter.
Place the orange round glass and knife on the edge of the table next to the small rock.
anns.task_desc: Grab a knife also an orange round glass, put the knife inside place the orange round glass on the kitchen counter.

high_descs: Turn around, go to the counter to the right of the stove top.
Pick up the knife next to the toaster from the counter.
Turn around, go to the sink on the right.
Put the knife in the gold wine glass next to the mug in the sink.
Pick up the wine glass from the sink.
Go to the front of the dishwasher which is to the left of the sink.
Put the wine glass on the counter to the front and left of the potato.
anns.task_desc: Put a wine glass with a knife in it on a counter.

high_descs: Turn around, turn left to face counter top where toaster is located.
Pick up knife, located behind the fork and to the left of the toaster.
Turn around, proceed to sink, turn right to face sink.
Place knife in goblet inside sink, standing up on its side.
Pick up goblet holding the knife from the sink.
Turn left and proceed to where counter with microwave is.  Turn right to face counter.
Place goblet on counter, to the left of the potato, the right of the spoon and in front of the bread.
anns.task_desc: Put a knife in a goblet, move both to a counter.

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the knife on the counter top to the left.
Pick up the knife from the counter top.
Turn around and walk to the sink on the right.
Put the knife inside the bronze cup which is in the sink basin.
Pick up the cup from the sink.
Turn left and walk to the counter top near the microwave.
Put the cup on the counter top, to the right of the spoon.
anns.task_desc: Put a cup with a knife in it on a counter top.

high_descs: Turn around and head towards the toaster on your left.
Pick up the knife to the left of the toaster.
Turn around and head towards the sink on your right.
Place the knife in the yellow cup in the sink.
Pick up the cup with the knife from the sink.
Take a step to the left to face the loaf of bread on the counter.
Place the cup in front of the bread.
anns.task_desc: Place a yellow cup with a knife in front of the bread on the counter.

high_descs: Move over to the counter with the knife and fork on it.
Pick up the knife from the counter.
Bring the knife over to the sink full of dishes.
Place the knife into the orange cup in the sink.
Pick up the orange cup with the knife in it.
Bring the orange cup over to the counter right of the microwave.
Put the orange cup on the counter to the right of the spoon.
anns.task_desc: Bring the orange cup with knife in it to the counter.
